===Talking to Fox with the makeshift poultice===
* '''Player:''' I have that poultice here for you.
* {{tbox|pic=Makeshift poultice detail.png|You give the poultice to Fox.}}
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Kuani! That's making a difference already.
* '''Player:''' Happy to help. Now, how did you get on finding what you needed to fix Kiko's bed?
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' I thought a little detour wouldn't hurt. I'd caught a glimpse of the most stunning pelt ever seen!
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' As I was tracking it, I was attacked and knocked out. When I came to, it was gone.
* '''Player:''' Gone?
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Without a trace, as well as most of my hunting equipment.
* '''Player:''' Do you think someone attacked you for it, or was it just an opportunist looting you?
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' I was unconscious.
* '''Player:''' Right, of course.
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' You've already done me a huge favour, but I don't suppose I could ask for one more small one?
* '''Player:''' I suppose I could. Especially if it goes towards repairing that cat's bed and getting you back to the guild.
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Well it's your lucky day! Make some room and I'll give you the sample needed to fix the bed.
** {{tact|end}}
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Well it's your lucky day! Take this sample to a woman called Atza in Outer Fortis. She'll have exactly what we need.
* '''Player:''' Where in the outskirts can I find her? And... what exactly do we need, again?
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' She lives by the south western gate of the city. She'll be able to give us the matching fur to repair the cat's bed with.
* {{tbox|pic=Fur sample detail.png|Fox gives you a fur sample.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Fox after giving him the poultice===
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' I thought a little detour wouldn't hurt. I'd caught a glimpse of the most stunning pelt ever seen!
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Fox before getting the fur sample with inventory space===
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Perfect! Here you go!
* {{tbox|pic=Fur sample detail.png|Fox gives you a fur sample.}}
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Fox again====
* {{tcond|If the player still has the fur sample or has a full inventory and not yet received the sample:}}
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Any success with Atza yet?
** '''Player:''' Not quite.
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' If you're struggling to find her, she's in Outer Fortis, near the south western gate.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player lost the fur sample and has a full inventory:}}
** '''Player:''' I appear to have lost the sample you gave me...
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Luckily, I always come prepared. Here's a spare.
** '''Player:''' Ah. It seems I don't have room for it.
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Well I'm not going anywhere. Let me know when you do have room.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player lost the fur sample:}}
** '''Player:''' I don't suppose you've got another sample of Kiko's bed for me to take to Atza?
** '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Fortunately for you, I'm always prepared... And our thief clearly didn't care for fine fur samples.
** '''Player:''' That's convenient! Usually I'm the one that's always ready for these situations.
** {{tbox|pic=Fur sample detail.png|Fox gives you a fur sample.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Guildmaster Apatura after giving Guild Hunter Fox the poultice===
* '''Guildmaster Apatura:''' Nilsal, hunter.
* '''Player:''' Nilsal, Apatura.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|quest=No|What do you do here?}}
* {{topt|Are you free to talk about my quest?}}
** '''Player:''' Are you free to talk about my quest?
** '''Guildmaster Apatura:''' Absolutely. How's it going, iknami?
