===Talking to Guild Hunter Wolf after giving Fox the poultice===
* '''Guild Hunter Wolf (Master):''' How's the Fox situation?
* '''Player:''' He's doing well. He's got me doing a few things for him whilst he recuperates.
* '''Guild Hunter Wolf (Master):''' Ha! Now that's the Fox I know. I'll have to give him some odd jobs once he's back to make up for ones you're covering!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Guild Scribe Verity after giving Fox the poultice===
* '''Guild Scribe Verity:''' Any updates on Fox?
* '''Player:''' I'm still working on it, but I'm getting there.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Atza===
* '''Player:''' Hi there. You must be Atza. I heard you're the person to talk to about getting some material to match a sample?
* '''Atza:''' I might be. Depends who's asking... and what you're looking for, of course.
* '''Player:''' Your friend Fox was going to bring this sample to you, but he's been a little... waylaid.
* '''Atza:''' Well, this wouldn't be the first time! Let's take a look.
* {{tcond|If the player lost the sample:}}
** '''Player:''' I don't seem to have it with me.
** '''Atza:''' You'll have to go back to Fox and grab it then.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tbox|pic=Fur sample detail.png|You give the fur sample to Atza.}}
* '''Player:''' Here you go.
* '''Atza:''' Good, good. Luckily for you, I recognise this fur. I do have a bit left, but I'll have to dig it out.
* '''Player:''' Shall I just wait here then?
* '''Atza:''' Oh... Fox usually helps me with my chores when he visits.
* '''Player:''' That's funny. He didn't mention that to me.
* '''Atza:''' That's alright, I'm sure a capable adventurer like you will manage fine. Fox was going to assemble some equipment for me. You can manage that, can't you?
* '''Player:''' I suppose so. Where do I start?
* '''Atza:''' It's all in that pile on the floor there. You can work it out, I'm sure.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Atza after giving her the fur===
* '''Atza:''' Now, luckily for you, I recognise this fur. I do have a bit left, but I'll have to dig it out.
* '''Player:''' Shall I just wait here then?
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Fox after giving Atza the material===
* '''Player:''' Hello again. I've given Atza the fur sample.
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' Did she give you the matching material?
* '''Player:''' Not yet. I should check back in with her.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Atza after she asks to set up the equipment===
* '''Atza:''' Don't forget, I need a hand setting up that equipment on the floor!
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'm on it.
* {{tact|end}}

===Setting up the pile of equipment without a hammer===
* {{tbox|pic=Hammer detail.png|You need a hammer to set up this equipment.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Setting up the pile of equipment===
* '''Atza:''' So anyway, how did you come to be doing this for Fox?
* '''Player:''' Well, he actually got attacked on his way over here.
* '''Atza:''' Shouldn't you be helping him heal up?
* '''Player:''' Oh he'll be alright. He was on the mend when I left him.
