* '''Atza:''' Oh, that's looking much better.
* '''Player:''' Now that's done, did you manage to find the material?
* '''Atza:''' Yes, I have it here.
* {{tbox|pic=Trimmed fur detail.png|Atza gives you some trimmed fur.}}
* '''Atza:''' Thanks for your help today. I hope that fur works for your project.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Atza after setting up the equipment===
* '''Player:''' Now that's done, did you manage to find the material?
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
** '''Atza:''' Yes, but you don't have enough room for it! Come back when you have space.
** {{tact|end}}
* '''Atza:''' Yes, I have it here.
* {{tbox|pic=Trimmed fur detail.png|Atza gives you some trimmed fur.}}

====Talking to Atza again====
* {{tcond|If the player lost the trimmed fur:}}
** '''Player:''' Could I get a replacement for that fur? I managed to lose it.
** '''Atza:''' You can, for now. I don't have an unlimited supply though, so be careful.
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** '''Atza:''' Ah, you don't have space for that.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tbox|pic=Trimmed fur detail.png|Atza gives you some trimmed fur.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player still has the trimmed fur:}}
** '''Atza:''' You should take that material back to Fox.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Fox===
* '''Player:''' Hello again. I got the fur from Atza. She's certainly... something.
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' She didn't make you do odd jobs for her, did she?
* '''Player:''' How did you know?
* '''Guild Hunter Fox:''' She does it every time I visit!
* {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
